WEBVTT

00:00:00.321 --> 00:00:05.095
(Telephone ringing)

00:00:05.410 --> 00:00:06.961
Adam Grant: Hello, this is Adam.

00:00:07.333 --> 00:00:08.532
Dave Chang: This is Dave.

00:00:08.556 --> 00:00:10.785
AG: Dave, I have to tell you
it's not every day

00:00:10.809 --> 00:00:13.420
that somebody invites
themselves on my podcast.

00:00:13.444 --> 00:00:15.630
DC: (Laughs) I'm willing to do anything,

00:00:15.654 --> 00:00:18.201
whatever it takes to be on this podcast.

00:00:18.225 --> 00:00:19.955
AG: OK, I'm going to interview you

00:00:19.979 --> 00:00:22.250
to see if you're qualified
for this opportunity.

00:00:22.274 --> 00:00:23.458
Tell me Dave,

00:00:23.482 --> 00:00:25.339
what's your greatest weakness?

00:00:25.363 --> 00:00:30.172
DC: My greatest weakness would
probably be my quick temper.